title: The Florida Gators had quite a few visitors on their campus
text:
The Florida Gators had quite a few visitors on their campus on Friday, but none were bigger than Jacksonville (Fla.) Trinity Christian five-star Tyreke Johnson . Living only 45 minutes north of Gainesville, the nations top rated safety for the 2018 class has been able to visit Florida quite a few times in the past.
On his most recent visit Johnson was able to meet with numerous coaches on staff including his area recruiter Tim Skipper .
